NUMBER 3856
NAME Black Tower, inside
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
An icy cold white mist covers the entire second story floor. The mist rolls
into the room from the chamber to the north in never-ending waves. Tiny blue
lights twinkle and disappear within the mist casting their small points of
light against the blackness of the tower walls. The effect makes it appear
that you are standing in the farthest reaches of space. The circular stone
stairway, in the center of the chamber, extends both upwards and downwards.
*DESCRIPTION_END
