NUMBER 3859
NAME Black Tower, small chamber
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Almost more of an alcove than a room, this tiny place seems to be a memorial
of some sort. A painting, draped in black bunting and illuminated on either
side by black candles, hangs on the far wall above a large wooden chest
decorated with images that a child might find amusing. The wall of webs to
the west offers no problem for you, as you know which path to take.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 3858
ITEM 0 345
EXTEND 0 draped in black bunting
ITEM 1 333 OPEN
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The black candles on either side of the painting cast their light over four
figures. In the foreground, holding hands and smiling happily are a small
boy and girl. Behind the two children, their hands resting lightly upon the
shoulders of the children, are a middle-aged man and woman. Both the man and
woman are smiling with joyful pride at the two children.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The chest is covered with fanciful carvings and paintings of unicorns,
knights and princesses.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM IN 1
The chest is mostly empty, except for a few broken remnants of toy soldiers
and dolls.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
NUMBER 3860
NAME Black Tower
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A few strands of silken cobwebs stretch from the corners of the room to
drape across the few furnishings the chamber contains. A small fireplace
rests in the west wall. Next to the fireplace is a bookshelf, containing
only a few volumes, all of which are covered with dust and cobwebs. A large
bed, with black silk sheets, has been pushed up against the northern wall,
while an impressively carved mirmach desk sits in the southern portion of
the room. A large, impressive painting hangs upon the wall above the
mantle of the fireplace. The bed is unmade and a chair is overturned behind
the desk, giving the impression that the occupant left his chambers in a
hurry.
*DESCRIPTION_END
